                <h3 style="font-size: 14px; color: #1A1A1A; margin: 0 0 12px;">
                  üìù Note
                </h3>
                <div style="background-color: #FAFAFA; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px;">
                  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666666; line-height: 1.6;">
                    {{ refund.note }}
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              {% endif %}

              <!-- CTA - Shop Again -->
              <div style="text-align: center; padding: 24px; background-color: #FAFAFA; border-radius: 12px;">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 15px; color: #1A1A1A;">
                  D√©sol√©s que cette commande ne vous ait pas convenu.<br>
                  On esp√®re vous revoir bient√¥t ! üíú
