                <a href="{{ shop.url }}/shop" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35 0%, #FF1493 100%); color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px;">
                  D√©couvrir nos nouveaut√©s
